txt.en: Use the Call Radhril skill and talk to Radhril

'Do you hear that? The footsteps of Men approach. Our time of rest is at its end. Let us prepare ourselves for combat, [placeholder]. The footsteps grow louder now. I hear them from all sides, converging on the docks.'
Get into position to defend Trader's Wharf!
Use the summoning horn at Trader's Wharf to summon Radhril to your side.
You should talk to Radhril.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>If Radhril is missing, and the Call Radhril skill is not available, try using the /pet release command.</rgb>
You should get into position to defend Trader's Wharf.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>If Radhril is missing, and the Call Radhril skill is not available, try using the /pet release command.</rgb>
You have been tasked with guarding Trader's Wharf from potential threats.
'I commend your efforts, [placeholder]! Come, let us return and report our success to the Free Peoples.'
You should defend Trader's Wharf from the attackers.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>If Radhril is missing, and the Call Radhril skill is not available, try using the /pet release command.</rgb>
